to connect s3 to ec2

1. creaate s3
2. create ec2
3. create IAM role to selectpolicy s3full access select and then add tag key name
4. update iam role in modify IAM role in ec2
5. thats it connection connected

how to access

1. open ec2 instance terminal 
2. update server    - sudo apt-get update
3. install aws    - sudo apt-get install awscli
4.   - aws s3 ls                     <-------------- this will show s3 bucket files
